<p>1. 若客戶選用本公司之服務, 所有已付款項均不設退款; 而在簽證批出後終止聘請, 須額外賠償本公司$3000 行政費用。<br>2. 若傭工申請簽證期間或到港前終止聘請，客戶可另選傭工, 不另收費, 而揀選其他國籍或不同服務, 須另付差額。<br>3. 若客戶在簽證申請期間更換其他傭工, 須另付$1800 文件費及行政費。 (已包合約費)<br>4. 若客戶取消申請, 服務費將可保留1 年內以簽署協議條款日計, 其款項可轉讓親友或朋友,如已入合約須支付$1800 合約費, 期後, 視為自<br>動放棄申請權利。<br>5. 每年政府有可能調整外傭最低工資及膳食津貼，如處理中的文件及暫未遞交至領事館辦理合約之客戶,須按政府公報日有須要調整外<br>傭最新工資 。<br>6. 傭工工作簽証取決於護照有效期, 如不足2 年, 需續餘下簽証, 費用為$350 由客戶支付。<br>7. 若傭工簽證生效後, 客戶須替傭工購買勞工保險及相關醫療保險 。<br>8. 若提交文件至領事館前, 傭工須通過身體檢查, 以確實身體狀況適合工作, 否則, 可另選傭工, 不另收費。<br>9. 菲律賓政府規定的外傭強制保險, 一經付款後, 客戶不能退回、轉名或中止保險。<br>10. 如因個別國家之政策變更而導致傭工不能出國，本公司將不會作任何賠償，但客戶可補回差價另聘其他國籍傭工。<br>11. 由於機票價格浮動，如果客戶指定抵港日期，將收取附加費。<br>12. 若傭工在到港後未能通過香港體檢, 本司將安排傭工回國, 客戶可另選傭工及本司會豁免文件費。( 須另付合約費 $800,簽証費$230, 機<br>票費 $1500, 體檢費 $600 及接機費$250 : 總額: $3380)<br>13. 傭工到港後可暫留本司4 天代辦身份證及驗身, 逾期後, 本司收取客戶傭工住宿費每天$150; 本司可送傭工到指定地鐵站或在公司給予<br>客戶。<br>14. 傭工所提供的個人資料、到港年份均能核實有效文件, 其海外或在港工作經驗、學歷、工作能力均由傭工及當地中介提供, 客戶在揀選<br>過程中可直接查詢傭工以確實資料。<br>15. 在提交申請期間，如傭工有隠瞞事實經相關部門發現而影響批核過程，客戶可另選傭工，將不另收費﹔而傭工到港後,發現有隠瞞事<br>實,客戶必須按本公司更換傭工條款替換傭工及按照香港&lt;僱傭法例>第57 章處理解約。<br>16. 若有關部門發現，客戶所提供的個人資料有誤導、虛報成份或其他個人問題而影響批核過程甚至申請被拒,本公司概不負責。<br>17. 所有有關申請文件, 客戶簽名式樣必須一致，否則文件被有關部門退回而影響批核過程, 本公司概不負責。<br>18. 客戶可於首名傭工工作簽証生效一年內更換傭工, 須按本公司更換條款。<br>19. 由簽署日起生效，服務協議有效期為365 天。<br>更換條款及收費: 計劃 A – (OE/LE)<br>i. 1 年內與首名傭工終止合約日期為準，更換海外孟傭工，須繳交手續費$850 另付$3000 保證金。(總額Total: $3850)<br>ii. 1 年內與首名傭工終止合約日期為準，更換海外菲傭工，須繳交手續費$5973 另付$3000 保證金。(總額Total: $8973)<br>iii. 1 年內與首名傭工終止合約日期為準，更換海外印、斯、柬、泰傭工，須繳交手續費$5250 另付$3000 保證金。(總額Total: $8250)<br>iv. 首名傭工為孟加拉籍之客戶，如須更換菲、印傭, 可享有八折優惠。<br>(i) – (iv) 已包菲律賓政府管理保險費 $1123, 驗身費$600 及接機費$250。)<br>v. 1 年內與外傭終止合約日期為準，更換在港外傭以原價減收$1000 並送在港基本驗身。(已包$196 OWWA 費用).<br>vi. 若客戶在傭工到港前取消申請, 其手續費及保證金將不會退回。<br>vii. 保證金必須待新傭工到港後兩星期內, 僱主可以致電查詢及到其分店取回保證金支票。</p><p>1. Any payments made under any option will be strictly non-refundable, otherwise; furthermore, in the event that customers request a cancellation under after the<br>issuance of visa, additional penalty fee $3000 must be paid by the customer for administration fee;<br>2. If an applicant cancels their application before the issuance of a visa, customer are entitled to choose another applicant under the same price bracket without any<br>fees or in the event that customers want to choose an applicants from a higher price bracket, then the balance between the two price brackets must be paid.<br>3. If a customer changes an applicant before the issuance of a visa, customers must pay $1800 in order to new set documentation fee and administration fee. (Included<br>contract fee).<br>4. If the customer cancels the application, the service fee will be retained within 1 year on the date of signing the agreement. The service can be transferred to relatives<br>or friends. If the contract is completed, additional contract fee $1800 will be charged; Otherwise be deemed to have waived after 1 year.<br>5. The Government may adjust the minimum wage and food allowance of FDHs for every year, and if customer’s document in the process or has not yet submitted<br>contract to consulate are required to adjust the latest wages of FDHs in accordance with the Official Gazette.<br>6. The working visa depends on the applicant’s passport expiration date, if the passport expires within two years, the customer will be responsible to renew it, and all<br>associated fees: $350.<br>7. Customers are required to purchase labour insurance and medical insurance for applicants upon visa effectively.<br>8. An applicant should pass the Medical examination before under processing, assure of her health fit to work in Hong Kong. Otherwise, customers have to choose<br>another applicant for placement without any payment.<br>9. Under Filipino jurisdiction, all applicants are mandated by law to purchase insurance; this is non-refundable upon payment.<br>10. If applicants are unable to reach Hong Kong due to an act of god, political and policy reasons, this company will not be held responsible and will offer no refunds,<br>However, customers may switch to applicants from other countries provided they pay any price differences.<br>11. Due to the fluctuation of air ticket price, surcharge will be implemented if specific date of arrival in Hong Kong is requested by the customer.<br>12. If the applicant fails the medical examinations required in HK, our company will pay for the return ticket to the applicant. Customers will waive the service fee on<br>their next application process. (customers are still required to pay the following: Contract fee $800, visa fee $230, airfare fee of $1500, medical examinations $600<br>and a pickup fee of $250; total: $3380).<br>13. Any applicant that have arrived in Hong Kong after 4 days may be retrieved by our customers during our office hours, or alternatively, customers may request<br>deliverance of the helper to any MTR stations for a pick-up between 4:00 pm to 7:00 pm. After the four days, $150 per day will be charged as boarding house fee.<br>14. Customers must understand that all information is given by either the applicants themselves, or their corresponding agencies overseas, this company is merely<br>passing on the information, Customers are welcome to cross examine all information given through interviews facilitated by this company.<br>15. During the application process, if it is discovered that the applicants have lied on their applications, and as a result halted the application process, this company<br>will offer a change of applicant at no extra cost. However, if discrepancies are discovered after arrival of the helper upon Hong Kong, customers must follow<br>standard procedures on changing applicants and if case, customer have to terminate the contract with helper, should follow the Employment Ordinance Cap. 57.<br>16. This company will not be held responsible if information provided by customers are proved to be inconsistent or falsified; And if the process of application is<br>severely affected as a result and was rejected.<br>17. When signing any official documents for the application process, the signature used by our customers must remain consistent throughout the application process,<br>this company will not be held liable if the application process in unsuccessful, suspended or faces major delays due to inconsistent signatures.<br>18. Our company will provide replacement service within 1 year upon the first helper’s working visa effectively and customers must follow terms of replacement.<br>19. The effective duration of this agreement will be 365 days from the day of signature.<br>Terms of Replacement and Service Fee: Discounts of option A (OE/LE):<br>i. Within 1 year of termination, change to a Bangladeshi helper at service fee $850 with an additional $3000 deposit. (Total: $3850)<br>ii. Within 1 year of termination, change to a Filipino helper at the service fee $5973 with an additional $3000 deposit. (Total: $8973)<br>iii. Within 1 year of termination, change to an Overseas Indo, Thai, Sri Lankan Cambodia helper at the service fee $5250 with an additional $3000 deposit. (Total: $8250)<br>iv. Customers who hired Bangladeshi helpers as their first helper, should they want to switch to overseas Filipino, or Indonesian Helpers will be had discount 20%.<br>((i) –(iv) Filipino mandated insurance cost of $1123 included, health examination $600 and pick up fee of $250 also included)<br>v. Within 1 year of termination, change to a local domestic helper with a discount of $1000 and a health examination free of charge. (Include OWWA $196)<br>vi. If customer cancel prior to the applicant’s arrival, deposit and all related fees will not be refunded.<br>vii. Deposits will be refunded after 2 weeks of the arrival of the helper, please contact relative branches for collecting the deposit cheque.</p>